-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/N%E1%BA%A1p-l%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-4EyffTwcbEAdDPns9RKPdA">Nạp lương - 納涼</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Nh%E1%BA%A5t-Tr%E1%BB%A5-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-BVqfcXhfQ6c5RnIvHrwhdw">Nhất Trụ tự - 一柱寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-ZzgazbvW_31Yn18OxsV6nA">Tùng Thiện Vương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%C3%AAu-D%E1%BB%8Bch/Th%C3%A1i-li%C3%AAn-kh%C3%BAc/poem-6AfrtE9PzrytTnQ7LkKQaw">Thái liên khúc - 採蓮曲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%C3%AAu-D%E1%BB%8Bch/author-1Zi-jnBZOTtGhVGhP05YYQ">Tiêu Dịch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Vi%E1%BB%87t-n%E1%BB%AF-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-CZTwtD50NDNN2KRFJ1Zlwg">Việt nữ từ kỳ 3 - 越女詞其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br></div>	</div>
